comments: The strength was that Professor Lambert was very knowledgeable and cared a lot about teaching the course.

comments: Only take this if you're willing to put in the work to really understand all the papers and technical concepts that will be taught. Overall, it was a good experience for me. Professor Lambert was very kind, patient, and knowledgeable.
